        <guid>https://sysadmin.info.pl/en/blog/how-to-install-properly-a-virtual-machine-in-qemu-kvm/</guid>
        <description>In this video I explained how to properly install the QEMU KVM virtual machine. I provided two methods of installation and described in details how to make it work.preallocation=metadata – allocates the space required by the metadata but doesn’t allocate any space for the data. This is the quickest to provision but the slowest for guest writes. Read the article: https://www.jamescoyle.net/how-to/181&amp;amp;#8230;
model=virtio virtualport_type=openvswitch explained here: https://www.mankier.com/1/virt-instal&amp;amp;#8230;</description>
        
